
I'd rather not overwrite the original scripts so I've put mine in scripts/

from the base dir

make
make install




hawkDir=/home/jake/.github/jakewendt/HAWK

nohup ${hawkDir}/scripts/hawk_countKmers.bash --proper_pair_only --bam_quality 60 --source_path /raid/data/raw/CCLS/bam --unique_extension .recaled.bam >> countKmers.out 2>&1 &


Next step requires a gwas_info.txt in the format of ...

SAMPLE1	M	Case
SAMPLE2	F	Case
SAMPLE3	M	Control
SAMPLE4	F	Control

It doesn't have to be sorted.

nohup ${hawkDir}/scripts/hawk_runHawk.bash >> runHawk.out 2>&1 &



nohup ${hawkDir}/scripts/hawk_runAbyss.bash >> runAbyss.out 2>&1 &

